Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.73,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:18.15,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯燥又乏味吧  所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:22.62,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正拒绝掉咯  找回你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:24.34,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.71,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对谎言如果不干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:32.50,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不再陪你听甜言蜜语  在这狭小的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.34,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自己找出来的myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.02,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然而然会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.13,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的馊主意踢到一边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:44.92,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切由我全权做主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.29,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I say, I say my heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.97,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Driver 任我自由突进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.92,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾一切勇敢前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:56.05,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越一切「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.11,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HFF0000&}{\pos(40,45)}Don't you stop me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.15,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take it eazy, Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.51,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起分享大获全胜的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.58,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛开结果好坏 只收获快感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.21,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其开反省会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.27,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HFF0000&}{\pos(40,45)}Got back to wild
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.27,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如加快脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.54,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎一切都未曾体验 每次都是强人所难
